rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I wonder what kind of facility this
was. There are shelves that look like
they could hold a lot of things...

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0003
rows.name:
It doesn't seem to make
any sound, though...

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0101
rows.name:
The perfect amount of space, and shelves
that look easy to climb... What is this...
My body is tingling with anticipation.

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0103
rows.name: If it made a sound, I'd have played it.

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0201
rows.name:
Mo-mo! What a big building, mo!
Maybe this was a mansion, Mo-mo?

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0202
rows.name: This must be an organ, mo.

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0203
rows.name:
It seems some things are the
same as in our time, mo...

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0301
rows.name:
It is like a grand marketplace...
I wonder if they sold goods here.

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0302
rows.name:
This organ... It must have
once produced a fine sound.

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0401
rows.name:
What's this, shelves?
So it's a shop, then.

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0402
rows.name:
A shop bigger than my audience
chamber... What in the world
is going on here...?

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0403
rows.name: As I thought, it won't make a sound.

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0404
rows.name:
If it wasn't broken, I
would've played something...
